komentar:
The amount of PC gamers since GTA IV & GTA V has almost doubled.
38 Million PS5's sold & 22 Million XBSX/S sold.
1.8 Billion PC gamers.
60 million potential customers vs 1.8 billion. That's just crazy...
Rockstar isn't stupid but they are at the same time, while yes the game will definitely come to PC, they should have it out day 1 because of the revenue they're missing out on, PC is the number 1 platform for streamers (Streamers bring income to games by making viewers purchase it).
"Oh but there are hackers & pirates on PC"
if you've followed GTA history you'll know that Rockstar has done absolutely nothing to combat piracy or hackers on PC, not only do they allow 3 strikes on your account before permanently being banned they also removed 95% of their anticheat due to one of their own employees selling the source code for money, so usually you'd think a company would rectify that & fix their anticheat right? Nope not Rockstar.
Then when us PC players FINALLY build a safe haven from hackers with the help of cfx (FiveM Roleplay) rockstar has the audacity to buy that entire platform & development team, implement it into GTA VI & then completely keep PC players in the dark after buying the one & only platform we have left.
Rockstar treats PC players like absolute crap yet we're the very ones that helped their entire development team exist to this day! Rockstar wasn't even a company until after a year of GTA 1 being released on PC, we built the foundations to their company & now they're just throwing us under the bus.
Makes me so mad.
